    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "pipeline_detail",
      "x": 70, "y": 490,
      "width": 400, "height": 292,
      "text": "class MessagePipeline:\n  switchboard_pool: asyncpg.Pool\n  dispatch_fn: spawner.trigger\n  source_butler: \"switchboard\"\n  enable_ingress_dedupe: true\n  max_concurrent_sessions: 3\n  ContextVar per asyncio task  (cross-task isolation)\n\nClassification pipeline:\n  raw envelope\n  → signal extraction  (intent, entities, urgency)\n  → domain classification\n      finance  ·  travel  ·  health\n      relationship  ·  general (fallback)\n  → target butler selection\n  → multi-butler fan-out  (spans domains)\n\nConversation history strategies:\n  telegram / whatsapp → realtime\n    (last 15min OR last 30 msgs)\n  email → full chain (50k tokens)\n  api / mcp → none\n\nDedup: telegram: update_id  /  email: Message-ID\nFallback: text inference (single match)\nAmbiguous → route to general butler",
      "originalText": "class MessagePipeline:\n  switchboard_pool: asyncpg.Pool\n  dispatch_fn: spawner.trigger\n  source_butler: \"switchboard\"\n  enable_ingress_dedupe: true\n  max_concurrent_sessions: 3\n  ContextVar per asyncio task  (cross-task isolation)\n\nClassification pipeline:\n  raw envelope\n  → signal extraction  (intent, entities, urgency)\n  → domain classification\n      finance  ·  travel  ·  health\n      relationship  ·  general (fallback)\n  → target butler selection\n  → multi-butler fan-out  (spans domains)\n\nConversation history strategies:\n  telegram / whatsapp → realtime\n    (last 15min OR last 30 msgs)\n  email → full chain (50k tokens)\n  api / mcp → none\n\nDedup: telegram: update_id  /  email: Message-ID\nFallback: text inference (single match)\nAmbiguous → route to general butler",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 100322,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 100323,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
